<h2 class="mb-4 font-weight-bold ">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
<h5 class="mb-2 mt-3 font-weight-semibold">1. What is Kindmate?</h5>
<p>Kindmate is an app to create and manage fundraising activities developed by Wake It Up. This application has two
  sessions one for individual fundraising activities and one for regular fundraising organizations.</p>
<h5 class="mb-2 mt-3 font-weight-semibold">2. Who can start a project on Kindmate?</h5>
<p>Anyone can use Kindmate to launch their own fundraising projects, including individuals, student clubs or
  non-governmental organizations.</p>
