<h5 class="mb-2 mt-3 font-weight-semibold">4. How long does the browsing time take?</h5>
<p>Activities posted on Kindmate will take up to 12 hours for the information browsing process. Then them
  I will email back the individual / originator regarding the status of the campaign.</p>
<h5 class="mb-2 mt-3 font-weight-semibold">5. Does Kindmate charge a fee?</h5>
<p>Kindmate is free to create and maintain for all campaigns, only charges for specialized support services
  and the campaign owner's special requirements.</p>
<p>Kindmate's activities are being maintained based on the voluntary contributions of supporters.</p>
<h5 class="mb-2 mt-3 font-weight-semibold">6. What happens if I do not reach my goal of raising funds?</h5>
<p>You are solely responsible for your fundraising campaign and for the commitments made. You can refund for
  supporters on the list provided by Kindmate, or devise a new action plan for the money available.</p>
<h5 class="mb-2 mt-3 font-weight-semibold">7. When will I receive my donation?</h5>
<p>Kindmate will disburse the campaign within 2 business days of the end of the fundraising period. The
